flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Initialize Pointers i = 0, j = 0]
    B --> C{Is i < nums1.length AND j < nums2.length?}
    C -->|Yes| D{Are nums1[i] and nums2[j] equal?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Return nums1[i] as Common Value]
    D -->|No| F{Is nums1[i] < nums2[j]?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Increment i]
    F -->|No| H[Increment j]
    G --> C
    H --> C
    C -->|No| I[Return -1: No Common Value]
    E --> J[End]
    I --> J
